2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] ## Dashboard Apparatus — `@shardworks/dashboard-apparatus`
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] 
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] ### Package: `packages/plugins/dashboard/`
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] 
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] **CLI usage:** `nsg dashboard start [--port 4242] [--no-open]`
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] 
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] The apparatus exposes a single CLI-only tool that starts a local web server and opens the browser. The server runs until Ctrl+C.
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] 
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] ### Web UI tabs
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] 
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] | Tab | Contents |
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] |-----|----------|
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] | **Overview** | Guild name/version/settings, stat cards (writs, sessions, rigs, codexes), loaded plugin list with type badges |
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] | **Clerk** | Sortable writs table; filter by status/type; client-side title search; Post Commission modal; inline status transitions (accept/complete/fail/cancel) with optional resolution text; pagination |
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] | **Walker** | Rig table with visual engine pipeline (status dots + arrows), progress bar per rig; filter by rig status |
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] | **Animator** | Session table with status, provider, duration, token usage, and cost; filter by status; pagination |
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] | **Codexes** | Registered codex list with clone status and active draft count; all-drafts table below |
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] 
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] ### Architecture
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] 
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] - **HTTP server**: Node.js built-in `http` module — no external dependencies
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] - **REST API** at `/api/*`: reads from apparatus APIs and Stacks `readBook` for cross-plugin access
2026-04-03T01:41:07Z [anima] - **Graceful degradation**: works even when optional apparatus (animator, walker, codexes) are not installed — tabs show empty states rather than errors
2026-04-03T01:41:08Z [anima] - **Single-file SPA**: full HTML/CSS/JS embedded in the package, served inline
